<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Page introuvable — {{ status_code|default(404) }}</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --panel: #111827;
      --text: #e5e7eb;
      --muted: #9ca3af;
      --accent: #64b5f6;
      --accent-2: #8b5cf6;
      --btn-bg: #1f2937;
      --btn-hover: #374151;
      --shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 10% -10%, rgba(139,92,246,.15), transparent 60%),
                  radial-gradient(900px 500px at 120% 120%, rgba(100,181,246,.2), transparent 60%),
                  var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font: 16px/1.6 system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji";
    }
    .wrap {
      min-height: 100%;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 40px 16px;
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 720px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04), rgba(255,255,255,.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 36px 28px 8px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(900px 220px at 0% 0%, rgba(139,92,246,.18), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 220px at 100% 0%, rgba(100,181,246,.18), transparent 60%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04), transparent);
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .6ch;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(17,24,39,.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: .02em;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }
    .code {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fca5a5;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 14px 0 8px;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px);
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 0 28px 28px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .cta {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    .btn, .link {
      appearance: none;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .6ch;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--btn-bg);
      transition: background .15s ease, transform .06s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: var(--btn-hover); }
    .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }
    .btn.primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
    }
    .btn.primary:hover { filter: brightness(1.05); }
    .tips {
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: rgba(17,24,39,.5);
    }
    .mono { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
      :root {
        --bg: #f3f4f6;
        --panel: #ffffff;
        --text: #111827;
        --muted: #6b7280;
        --btn-bg: #f8fafc;
        --btn-hover: #eef2f7;
      }
      .card { border-color: rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
      .footer { border-top-color: rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <article class="card" role="alert" aria-live="polite">
      <header class="hero">
        <span class="badge" aria-label="Erreur HTTP">
          <span class="mono code">{{ status_code|default(404) }}</span>
          <span>Page introuvable</span>
        </span>
        <h1>Oups… Cette page n’existe pas ou a été déplacée.</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          {{ status_text|default('La ressource demandée est introuvable.') }}
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/" rel="home" aria-label="Retour à l’accueil">
            ⟵ Retour à l’accueil
          </a>
          <button class="btn" type="button" onclick="history.back()" aria-label="Revenir à la page précédente">
            ◀ Revenir en arrière
          </button>
        </div>
        <p class="tips">
          • Vérifiez l’URL saisie • Essayez depuis la page d’accueil • Si le problème persiste, réessayez plus tard.
        </p>
      </div>

      <footer class="footer">
        <span>Erreur <span class="mono">{{ status_code|default(404) }}</span></span>
        <span>Powered by Symfony</span>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
